Variabele `r c_var_names[i]`
----------------------------------------
The table shows the number of observations of each level.

``` {r results='asis'}
library(xtable)
xt <- xtable(table(c_data[c_var_names[i]]), caption = c_var_names[i])
names(xt) <- c('count')
print(xtable(xt),type='html')

```
